data.description: This Fully Available 2 bedroom, 2 bath townhouse offers Newer A/C (2020), newer washer and dryer (2021) and minutes to MacDill AFB!   This is a really GREAT OPPORTUNITY to make this townhome located in South Tampa your own!  It is within minutes to MacDill AFB and W. Gandy Boulevard for all of your shopping needs!  This unit offers NEWER A/C (2020) and NEWER WASHER AND DRYER (2021).  The building also had a new roof installed in 2017.  Schooner Cove is a GATED Community in South Tampa.  You will love one level living for convenient, easy living!  The eat in kitchen offers a breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances and a pantry.  The kitchen is open to the living room and dining area.  The master bedroom is spacious and offers a walk in closet, double sinks and a private washroom area.  The second bedroom is large and in close proximity to the second bath.  The baths are beautifully tiled and spacious. There is also a spacious one car garage that has plenty of room for your car and storage! Schooner Cove is a gated Community, which is minutes from MacDill AFB, schools, shopping and convenient to all highways. You will enjoy the amenities which include a pool, hot tub, gym and clubhouse.  The clubhouse can be rented for special events.  There are sidewalks throughout and a large lake to walk around. The HOA fee includes security gate, water, sewer, trash, recycling, pool, gym and clubhouse.
